snippet.title: BEFIKAR | Tanzeel Khan ft. Aashna Hegde
snippet.description:
GIVING YOU GUYS A PART OF OUR HEARTS WITH [ B E F I K A R ] 👫♥️

This song depicts young love, love that has no bounds! A song that’ll make you feel all the emotions, that’ll make you dance your heart away! So go enjoy this song with your loved ones, tell them you love them and always remember to love without any fikar, love Befikar!

#Befikar #TanzeelKhan #AashnaHegde

______________________________________
Audio
Artists : Tanzeel Khan & Aashna Hegde
Lyrics & Composition : Tanzeel Khan
Music : Akarsh Shetty
Mixing & Mastering : Hanish Taneja

Video
Director : Vaibhav Patil
Artist Manager/Line Producer : Dane Pereira
Production Manager : Ashish Guria
DOPs : Arun Sharma, Appu VS
Edit : Shubham Vasudev
Colour Grading & Sound Correction : Abhishek Kini
Crew : Aakash Chepya
MUA: Kausha Lodaliya

Location : Big Mama

______________________________________
Lyrics:

[Tanzeel]
Mera dil Meri jaaan
Mujhse na chupa
Chahat karde bayaaan
Mere dil ka kya? 

Dil mein hai baatein meri jo basi voh
Keh na saka mein tumse kabhi jo
Dena hai dil ab bas yeh tum hi ko
Chahat meri ab se tum hi ho

Kaise bhula du saari voh baatein
Khush bhi hu toh tere sahaare
Soye na ab hum kitni hi raatein
Paya hai tujko ab yeh jahan mein

Khwaabon mein tujhse milta raha
chah ke mein na keh yeh saka
Ki Tere bina kya wajood mera
hona nahi kabhi tujhse juda

(Hook) (X2)
Befikar hogaya 
mai kidhar kho gaya
Ishq ki raah me            
ab tu milgaya 

[Aashna]
Mera dil meri jaaan
Mujhsee na chupaaa
Chahat karde bayaan
Mere dil ka kya? 

Jaanu mein sab kuch ,jo tu chupaye 
Mere alava sabko bataye
Pyaar se haq mujhpe jo jataye 
Na jaane kyu itna tu sataye

Meri ye dhadkane be-sabar hai
Shayad tujhko bhi na khabar hai
Mere liye tu kitna alag hai
Teri chahat ki bhi samjh hai


Khwaabon mein tujhse milti rahi
Chah ke bhi kuch keh na saki , 
Jo Aaj bhi mein tujhme hi basi
Jaana na ab tu door kahi 

(Hook) x2
Befikar ho gaya 
Mai kidhar kho gaya
Ishq ki raah me               
Ab tu mil gaya

snippet.title: India's GDP Crash: Act of God? Or Act of Fraud? | The Deshbhakt with Akash Banerjee
snippet.description:
Shoutout to Kuvera! - Download the app: http://bit.ly/2Xo9Jly

India's gross domestic product or GDP contracted by a massive MINUS 23.9% in the April-June period, that is what the official NSO data said. The data revealed that majority of the sectors are hit by a negative growth after the lockdown - making this the worst economic stump in India and also the in the world amongst big economies.

However in this edition of the deshbhakt we are going to take a look at how India's GDP was anyways on a downward spiral BEFORE the virus struck - making the cut deeper for India than any other country. Even before the lockdown, GDP growth was declining since the last eight quarters.

The Finance Minister has already said that this time, the decline in growth is an ‘act of God’ - however data shows that an act of Fraud has been committed and this depression is not going away any time soon.

snippet.title: EMIWAY - THANKS TO GOD (Prod. by Pendo46) (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Lyrics given below

Artist & Lyrics - Emiway Bantai 

Music - Pendo46
https://www.youtube.com/user/Rillataan

Mix/Master - Emiway

Visuals by - Happy

Edited by -  Happy and Emiway

Production - Bantai studio 

Producer- Emiway Bantai

Emiway Management MAIL ID 
imailemiway@gmail.com

Social connect
Instagram - Emiway_Bantai
Facebook - Emiway37
Twitter - emiwaytweets

(Lyrics)
Ab mei accha karra tha
Abba ka kam hora tha thap par woh nai har manenge
Woh badalke rhenge kismat
Filal jo waqt tha woh kaagi saqt tha paisa usane se pehle deraha hu sadqah.Mujhe rehna hai strong Dhyan rakhna hai sabka pata bhi nai chala achanak se kaise tapka pareshani,chod gaya nishani yeah.Aj gana nai sunane aya hu kahani mei.

Subha ka waqt tha
Abba ke sar mei dard tha
Raat ko sone se pehle unke dil mei dar tha
Mummy ka call aya subhe boli woh jaldi se ghar aa
Mei bhagke jake dekha
Abba ka halat bigadta ja rha tha
andhar ka dard aj chehre pe dikha
Raha tha
Kha par leke jau kuch nhi smjh aa rha tha
Aese tese karke le gaya unko aspatal
Ek nai do nai teen nai char
Dekha nai tha unka aisa haal
Leke gaya unhe ambulance mei
Baithke
Pehchan nai rhe the abba
Mujhe dekhke
Mei dekhta hi rehgaya
Kafi din se roya nai tha lekin usdin behgaya
Malik pe tab bhi bharosa tha mei unse kehgaya
Man hi man mei
Mere abba ko lota do
Unke sapne ko pura karne ko firse ek mauka do
Theekh kaise karu mei unhe
rasta koi
Batado
Abba ko bachalo

Aisa lagra tha
Abba yad dash kho diye
Icu mei dekheke unhe ammi
Bhi roo diye
Par har nahi mane hum
Pata tha woh
Lotenge
Bure khayalat are the
Lekin hum
Rokenge
Chokenge jab dekhenge
Bhagwan ka karishma
Mei tut rha tha
Mujhe lagne laga sadma
Par anu ballu bhai Sumit minta
Shabana didi sab sath the
Family walo ne dia sath
Bole khuda sath hai

Sath hai khuda mere sath hai
Zindagi hai hi aisi cheez din
Kabhi raat hai (x3)
Sath hai sath hai khuda sabke
sath hai zindagi hai aisi cheez
Din kabhi raat hai kya

Alhumdulillah
All praises to allah
Almighty god is great
He is the greatest

Sabke bech rehke bhi akela pan sa mehsoos tha
Stress badnelaga tha
Mei thoda sa confuse tha
Par khoya nahi meine khudko
Shayat soch mei dalneki
Koshish mei hai
Rukko
Jao jhukko
Aur matha teko
Khudake saamne
Madad karenge teri woh khud aake samne
Aameen
Par jo hua hai usse meine kafi kuch seekha hai
Khush rehna seekhle
Khudse kyu roota hai
andhar se toota
Uthna majboot hoga
Zindagi mei
Aisa kabhi nai bolna ke zindagi hai meri
Gandagi mei
Jo bhi hota hai sab ke peeche kuch na kuch wajah
Dukhi tha mei 3 din
Lekin aj firse maza
aane laga hai
Abba pure theekh hogaye
Teri raza hai
Takleefo se ladke aur aage
Chala gaya mei
Kal toota tha lekin
Aj bilkul naya mei
Mei laut aya hu tere pass
Kaha tha chala gaya mei

#thankstogod #emiwaybantai #universe

snippet.title: Brandy and Monica go head-to-head in Verzuz
snippet.description:
One of the fiercest modern day diva showdowns came to a head Monday tonight (Aug. 31) as R&B legends Brandy and Monica faced off in the ultimate Verzuz battle. Hosted live at Tyler Perry Studios, the two vocal giants played their top hits for over 1 million fans — who joined the party within just the first 30 minutes. Stars like Keke Palmer, Fantasia, Bryan Michael Cox, Missy Elliott, Johnta Austin, Solange and Jimmy Jam even tuned in to watch the celebration of over 20 years of musical mastery. 

The livestream began promptly with a DJ mix of Atlanta artists to get the crowd warmed up for the main event presented by Ciroc in partnership with Live Nation initiative Femme It Forward. Then, the real battle began... and the rest was Verzuz history.

snippet.localized.title: Brandy and Monica go head-to-head in Verzuz
snippet.localized.description:
One of the fiercest modern day diva showdowns came to a head Monday tonight (Aug. 31) as R&B legends Brandy and Monica faced off in the ultimate Verzuz battle. Hosted live at Tyler Perry Studios, the two vocal giants played their top hits for over 1 million fans — who joined the party within just the first 30 minutes. Stars like Keke Palmer, Fantasia, Bryan Michael Cox, Missy Elliott, Johnta Austin, Solange and Jimmy Jam even tuned in to watch the celebration of over 20 years of musical mastery. 

The livestream began promptly with a DJ mix of Atlanta artists to get the crowd warmed up for the main event presented by Ciroc in partnership with Live Nation initiative Femme It Forward. Then, the real battle began... and the rest was Verzuz history.

Watch Brandy and Monica's Verzuz above! #Brandy #Monica #Verzuz

snippet.title: Michael B. Jordan Is 'Struggling' After Chadwick Boseman's Death
snippet.description: ET has learned Michael B. Jordan is having a difficult time following the tragic death of his friend and 'Black Panther' co-star, Chadwick Boseman. The ‘42’ star died last week following a private, 4-year-long battle with colon cancer. Following the news of his death, some of his Marvel co-stars, including Angela Bassett and Sterling K. Brown, paid tribute to the late star on social media.

All stages are also live streamed on a dedicated app, NBC Sports Gold. NBCSN features live coverage of some of America’s biggest cycling events including the AMGEN Tour of California and the Critérium du Dauphiné, in addition to the Paris Roubaix, Liège-Bastogne-Liège and, one of the most important stage races, the Paris-Nice.

snippet.title: SAOCOM 1B Mission
snippet.description:
SpaceX is targeting Sunday, August 30 at 7:18 p.m. EDT, or 23:18 UTC, for Falcon 9’s launch of the SAOCOM 1B mission, which will carry the SAOCOM 1B spacecraft to orbit in addition to two rideshare payloads, Tyvak-0172 and PlanetiQ’s GNOMES-1. The mission will lift off from Space Launch Complex 40 (SLC-40) at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station in Florida. A backup launch opportunity is available on Monday, August 31 at 7:19 p.m. EDT, or 23:19 UTC. This mission marks SpaceX’s first launch to a polar orbit from the East Coast, and the first polar launch from Florida in decades.

Falcon 9’s first stage previously launched Dragon to the International Space Station for SpaceX’s 19th and 20th commercial resupply missions, and it also supported launch of SpaceX’s ninth Starlink mission. Following stage separation, SpaceX will land Falcon 9 on Landing Zone 1 at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station. SAOCOM 1B will deploy approximately 14 minutes after launch, GNOMES-1 and Tyvak-0172 will deploy approximately 61 and 62 minutes after liftoff.

snippet.title: First Look At The Stand, A CBS All Access Limited Event Series Based On The Novel By Stephen King
snippet.description:
Based on the best-selling novel by Stephen King, CBS All Access's The Stand stars Whoopi Goldberg, Alexander Skarsgård, James Marsden, Odessa Young, Jovan Adepo, and many more. The limited event series will also feature an all-new coda written by Stephen King. Don't miss the premiere of The Stand on Thursday, Dec. 17, streaming exclusively on CBS All Access.

snippet.title: What if the Byzantine Empire Survived?
snippet.description:
Create your own 'What If' meme: https://bit.ly/2CH52P8  Contest is still going on!

The Eastern Romans survived for a millennia after the fall of the West before their own demise from the Ottomans. The sack of Constantinople is often thought as the end of the Medieval Age and the start of another. Politics of the past forgotten. So what if in an alternate timeline this never happened? What if the Byzantine Empire actually survived, and continued on? Here is one scenario.

snippet.title: Clash Royale: ⚔️ CLAN WARS 2 IS HERE! ⚔️ (Official Launch Trailer)
snippet.description:
NEW UPDATE! CLAN WARS 2!
- Sail your Clan Boat towards rewards & glory
- Join the River Race and go head-to-head with other Clans for huge rewards
- Set up your Boat Defenses and attack other Clan Boats in naval Boat Battles
- Build 4 War Decks and take on other players in high-stakes Duels
PLAY NOW! 

Subscribe for more! ►► http://supr.cl/SubRoyale
Enter the Arena! From the creators of Clash of Clans comes a real-time multiplayer game starring the Royales, your favorite Clash characters and much, much more. 

Collect and upgrade dozens of cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defenses you know and love, as well as the Royales: Princes, Knights, Baby Dragons and more. Knock the enemy King and Princesses from their towers to defeat your opponents and win Trophies, Crowns and glory in the Arena. Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community.

FEATURES
• Duel players from around the world in real-time in both 1v1 and 2v2 Battles
• Earn chests to unlock rewards, collect powerful new cards and upgrade existing ones
• Destroy opponent's towers and win Crowns to earn epic Crown chests
• Build and upgrade your card collection with the Clash Royale Family along with dozens of your favorite Clash troops, spells and defenses
• Construct your ultimate Battle Deck to defeat your opponents
• Progress through multiple Arenas all the way to the top
• Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community
• Challenge your Clanmates and friends to a private duel, or play side-by-side in a 2v2 Battle
• Work together with your Clan to unlock Clan Chests
• Play new events every week
• Learn different battle tactics by watching the best duels on TV Royale

PLEASE NOTE! Clash Royale is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash Royale. A network connection is also required.

Support:
Are you having problems? Visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clash-royale/ or contact us in-game by going to Settings, Help and support.
Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/
Terms of Service:
http://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/
Parent's Guide:
http://supercell.com/en/parents/

Supercell and Clash Royale are trademarks of Supercell oy

snippet.title: Surviving the Hottest Place in the World
snippet.description:
Go to http://www.audible.com/yestheory or text yestheory to 500 500 to get one free audiobook, unlimited Audible originals and a 30-day free trial
New Seek Discomfort Summer Drop: https://www.seekdiscomfort.com/ live for only 72hrs!

This week after Death Valley hit the hottest temperature ever recorded... We decided to go and experience what 130F or 56C felt like... Both the best and worst idea we've ever had.

Does anyone read the description? I never really know to be honest. Well either way, this is Thomas and I'm a bit bored writing this so I'll just keep typing random things and see if anybody will notice. Conor was really upset that we kept him farting in the video so please ignore that part (or don't). Anyways, hope you liked the video we're actually pretty stoked with how it came out!

Check out Conor's channel here and tell him we sent you it'll make him very happy!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1E5Ti2P70zZxA4osS2MhiA

Thank you to Tommy, Tristan and Nathan for tagging along as our rescue team.

We have a 2nd channel! Make sure to subscribe to it here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTd7KzdwnFE3lm6LCfYDmUQ

If you want to join the Yes Fam Facebook group which is 100,000+ of our most engaged and badass community members, you can apply here: 
https://www.facebook.com/groups/yesfam/

PERFECT ROYALTY FREE MUSIC FOR YOUTUBE: free 30 day trial here: http://share.epidemicsound.com/wFFbr 

Musicbed has amazing montage and cinematic music:
http://share.mscbd.fm/YesTheory

For an amazing b-roll and footage library, checkout: http://storyblocks.com/YesTheory

Yes Theory Spotify Playlist: 
https://open.spotify.com/user/t-boogy...

Exclusive challenges on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/yestheory/

Who are we? 
We believe that life can be as fulfilling as you wish, so long as you're willing to seek discomfort. And we make videos about it.

Business Inquiries: zack@yestheory.com
For community inquiries: hello@yestheory.com

https://www.instagram.com/yestheory/
https://twitter.com/yestheory
https://www.facebook.com/yestheory/

Produced by Lauren Rosen

snippet.title: Overhyped or AWESOME? | Vice Golf Ball Review
snippet.description:
Overhyped or AWESOME? | Vice Golf Ball Review
PGA GOLF PRO Rick Shiels tests out the Vice Pro Plus golf balls. Rick Shiels went online to pick which Vice Golf Balls would suit his game. Rick tests out the Vice Golf Ball on the golf course at Marriott Worsley Park Golf Club, tests the golf balls for spin, feel, durability, distance and much more! 

Rick Shiels is also giving away 2 dozen golf balls both on YouTube and Facebook. 

https://www.facebook.com/253446978180761/posts/1438990602959720/

►Become a FREE SUBSCRIBER to RICK SHIELS now 
http://bit.ly/SubRickShielsGolf

► Official Apparel and footwear partner: Nike Golf 
http://www.nike.com/golf

►Official Garmin Ambassador: 
https://explore.garmin.com/en-GB/golf/

► Hit #Subscribe & #HitTheBell so you don't miss out on any new videos! 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
►My Links:
Facebook  ► https://www.facebook.com/RickShielsPGA/
Twitter       ► http://bit.ly/RickShielsTwitter
Instagram ► http://bit.ly/RickShielsIG
Web           ► http://www.rickshielsgolf.co.uk/
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Hi I’m Rick Shiels, welcome to my channel RickShielsPGAGolf. This YouTube channel is designed to help you play better golf, also to help you enjoy your golf more! 

I specialise in golf club reviews, golf club unboxing, golf club news, golf club head to heads, and all about golf clubs. 

I also want to make you play better golf by providing coaching video on all topics about golf, how to fix your slice, fix your hook, help you drive the golf ball longer, hit your irons more pure, hit your irons closer to the hole and help you draw and fade your golf shots. 
I will also help you lower your score by chipping better by stopping you duff and thin chips, pitch the ball closer and also create backspin. Also I will provide you help to putt better and hole more putts! 

On this channel I also make fun and entertaining golf content based on crazy and sometimes “gimmicky” golf clubs. I like to cut through the marketing hype about products and I like to give you the honest truth about golf equipment. 

If you enjoy the channel make sure you hit subscribe and also tap the notification bell so that you are always notified when I release a new video.

snippet.title: Mariah Carey on ‘Ellen’ Outing Her Pregnancy in 2008
snippet.description: In a new interview with ‘Vulture,’ Mariah Carey opens up about her ‘extremely uncomfortable’ appearance on ‘The Ellen Degeneres Show’ back in 2008, when the TV personality tried to offset rumors that the singer was pregnant by having her drink champagne. The clip recently resurfaced on Twitter amidst an ongoing investigation of the show following allegations that it’s a ‘toxic’ workplace environment.

snippet.title: Brandy and Monica go head-to-head in Verzuz
snippet.description:
One of the fiercest modern day diva showdowns came to a head Monday tonight (Aug. 31) as R&B legends Brandy and Monica faced off in the ultimate Verzuz battle. Hosted live at Tyler Perry Studios, the two vocal giants played their top hits for over 1 million fans — who joined the party within just the first 30 minutes. Stars like Keke Palmer, Fantasia, Bryan Michael Cox, Missy Elliott, Johnta Austin, Solange and Jimmy Jam even tuned in to watch the celebration of over 20 years of musical mastery. 

The livestream began promptly with a DJ mix of Atlanta artists to get the crowd warmed up for the main event presented by Ciroc in partnership with Live Nation initiative Femme It Forward. Then, the real battle began... and the rest was Verzuz history.

Watch Brandy and Monica's Verzuz above! #Brandy #Monica #Verzuz

The ‘42’ star died last week following a private, 4-year-long battle with colon cancer. Following the news of his death, some of his Marvel co-stars, including Angela Bassett and Sterling K. Brown, paid tribute to the late star on social media.

snippet.title: Christina Aguilera - Reflection (2020)/Loyal Brave True Medley (From "Mulan")
snippet.description:
Stream Disney’s Mulan September 4 exclusively on Disney+ with Premier Access. Additional fee required. More info: http://disneyplus.com/mulan

“Reflection”
Performed by Christina Aguilera (@xtina) From Mulan (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) Download/stream it here: https://disneymusic.co/Mulan?iqid=dmvevo ⚔ 

⚔ ⚔ When the Emperor of China issues a decree that one man per family must serve in the Imperial Army to defend the country from Northern invaders, Hua Mulan, the eldest daughter of an honored warrior, steps in to take the place of her ailing father. Masquerading as a man, Hua Jun, she is tested every step of the way and must harness her inner-strength and embrace her true potential. It is an epic journey that will transform her into an honored warrior and earn her the respect of a grateful nation…and a proud father. “Mulan” features a celebrated international cast that includes: Yifei Liu as Mulan; Donnie Yen as Commander Tung; Jason Scott Lee as Böri Khan; Yoson An as Cheng Honghui; with Gong Li as Xianniang and Jet Li as the Emperor. The film is directed by Niki Caro from a screenplay by Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver and Elizabeth Martin & Lauren Hynek based on the narrative poem “The Ballad of Mulan.”

snippet.title: What if the Byzantine Empire Survived?
snippet.description:
Create your own 'What If' meme: https://bit.ly/2CH52P8  Contest is still going on!

The Eastern Romans survived for a millennia after the fall of the West before their own demise from the Ottomans. The sack of Constantinople is often thought as the end of the Medieval Age and the start of another. Politics of the past forgotten. So what if in an alternate timeline this never happened? What if the Byzantine Empire actually survived, and continued on? Here is one scenario.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/AltHistoryHub
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/AlternateHistoryHub

Глубоко в тропических джунглях находятся висячие королевства красивых и смертоносных мастеров: Они что-то вроде высших эльфов муравьиного царства: Талантливые архитекторы, создающие дворцы и города. Помимо этого, они яростные и экспансивные воины, чьи королевства постоянно поглощены нескончаемым боем за выживание. Муравьи-ткачи экофилла.

snippet.title: Sexual Harassment | Real Talk Season 2 Episode 4
snippet.description:
How would you know you’re being sexually harassed?

In this episode, the cast speak up about their unfortunate experience of being sexually harassed and give advice on what we should do if such a thing were to happen, not only to us, but to others as well.

If you have experienced any form of sexual harassment and are in need of help, please visit:

Sexual Assault Care Centre
http://sacc.aware.org.sg/

AWARE Singapore
https://www.aware.org.sg/

Subscribe for more content like this: http://bit.ly/SubscribeMOSG 

Catch more Millennial Stories here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTiPyDtowSLTa8zPJKxY5G4Xcfknkabzd

Catch more Real Talk episodes here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTiPyDtowSLS_oGC6b8MuUfNjynhZnA4i

snippet.description:
Stream Disney’s Mulan September 4 exclusively on Disney+ with Premier Access. Additional fee required. More info: http://disneyplus.com/mulan

“Reflection”
Performed by Christina Aguilera (@xtina) From Mulan (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) Download/stream it here: https://disneymusic.co/Mulan?iqid=dmvevo ⚔ 

⚔ ⚔ When the Emperor of China issues a decree that one man per family must serve in the Imperial Army to defend the country from Northern invaders, Hua Mulan, the eldest daughter of an honored warrior, steps in to take the place of her ailing father. Masquerading as a man, Hua Jun, she is tested every step of the way and must harness her inner-strength and embrace her true potential. It is an epic journey that will transform her into an honored warrior and earn her the respect of a grateful nation…and a proud father. “Mulan” features a celebrated international cast that includes: Yifei Liu as Mulan; Donnie Yen as Commander Tung; Jason Scott Lee as Böri Khan; Yoson An as Cheng Honghui; with Gong Li as Xianniang and Jet Li as the Emperor. The film is directed by Niki Caro from a screenplay by Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver and Elizabeth Martin & Lauren Hynek based on the narrative poem “The Ballad of Mulan.”

localizations.ru.description:
Подписывайтесь на @KDA_MUSIC в Twitter и Instagram, чтобы всегда быть в курсе новостей.

Они пришли устроить шоу. Группа K/DA возвращается с новым предрелизным синглом THE BADDEST, в записи которого принимали участие вокалисты SOYEON и MIYEON из (G)I-DLE, Беа Миллер и Wolftyla.

K/DA – это виртуальная группа, основанная Ари, Эвелинн, Акали и Кай'Сой. В 2018 году они дебютировали с хитом POP/STARS и теперь возвращаются с долгожданным мини-альбомом, который скоро будет доступен для прослушивания.

Sabemos que te impresiona. Sé testigo del regreso de K/DA con el nuevo sencillo previo al lanzamiento: ''THE BADDEST'', con las voces de las talentosas SOYEON y MIYEON de (G)I-DLE; Bea Miller, y Wolftyla.

K/DA es un supergrupo musical virtual conformado por Ahri, Evelynn, Akali y Kai'Sa. Después de su explosivo debut ''POP/STARS'', K/DA regresa este año con su muy esperado EP, disponible próximamente.

localizations.cs.description:
Sledujte @KDA_MUSIC na Twitteru a Instagramu, kde najdete novinky každý den.

Je to vychloubání. Sledujte comeback K/DA s předpremiérovým singlem „THE BADDEST“, na kterém se podílejí zpěváci SOYEON a MIYEON z (G)I-DLE, Bea Miller a Wolftyla.

K/DA je virtuální hudební superskupina, kterou tvoří Ahri, Evelynn, Akali a Kai’Sa. Po výbušném debutu „POP/STARS“ se K/DA letos vracejí s dlouho očekávanou deskou, která vyjde brzy.

localizations.hu.description:
A friss napi hírekért kövesd a @KDA_MUSIC-ot a Twitteren és az Instagramon.

Csak felvágás? Légy szemtanúja, hogyan tér vissza a K/DA a „THE BADDEST” című új kislemezével, amely a (G)I-DLE tagjai, SOYEON és MIYEON, valamint Bea Miller és Wolftyla közreműködésével készült.

A K/DA egy virtuális zenei szupercsapat, amelynek tagja Ahri, Evelynn, Akali és Kai’Sa. A sikeres „POP/SZTÁROK” bemutatkozószámuk után a K/DA visszatér a régóta várt középlemezzel – hamarosan.

localizations.ja.description:
twitter、Instagramで @KDA_MUSIC をフォローして最新情報を手に入れよう。

SOYEON、MIYEON of (G)I-DLE、Bea Miller、そしてWolftylaをフィーチャーした先行シングル「THE BADDEST」で K/DA が華麗なる復活を魅せつける。

K/DA：「POP/STARS」で鮮烈なデビューを飾った、アーリ、イブリン、アカリ、カイ＝サからなるバーチャルミュージックスーパーユニット。最新のシングルで待望の復活を果たした。

https://jp.leagueoflegends.com/ja-jp/event/kda-official-fan-club/

localizations.el.description:
Ακολουθήστε το @KDA_MUSIC σε Twitter και Instagram για καθημερινές ενημερώσεις.

Πείτε ότι την έχουμε ψωνίσει. Ζήστε την επιστροφή των K/DA με το single πριν την κυκλοφορία, «THE BADDEST», με τις φωνές των SOYEON και MIYEON και (G)I-DLE, Bea Miller και Wolftyla.

Οι K/DA είναι ένα εικονικό, σούπερ μουσικό συγκρότημα με τις Άρι, Έβελιν, Ακάλι και Κάι'Σα. Μετά το εκρηκτικό τους ντεμπούτο «POP/STARS», οι K/DA επιστρέφουν φέτος με ένα πολυαναμενόμενο άλμπουμ, που θα κυκλοφορήσει σύντομα.

snippet.title: The Batman - DC FanDome Teaser
snippet.description:
Robert Pattinson is #TheBatman.

https://www.instagram.com/thebatman/
https://www.facebook.com/thebatman
https://twitter.com/thebatman
http://thebatman.com

From Warner Bros. Pictures comes “The Batman,” with director Matt Reeves (the “Planet of the Apes” films) at the helm and with Robert Pattinson (“Tenet,” “The Lighthouse,” “Good Time”) starring as Gotham City’s vigilante detective, Batman, and billionaire Bruce Wayne.

Also in the star-studded ensemble as Gotham’s famous and infamous cast of characters are Zoë Kravitz (“Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald,” “Mad Max: Fury Road”) as Selina Kyle; Paul Dano (“Love & Mercy,” “12 Years a Slave”) as Edward Nashton; Jeffrey Wright (the “Hunger Games” films) as the GCPD’s James Gordon; John Turturro (the “Transformers” films) as Carmine Falcone; Peter Sarsgaard (“The Magnificent Seven,” “Black Mass”) as Gotham D.A. Gil Colson; Barry Keoghan (“Dunkirk”) as Officer Stanley Merkel; Jayme Lawson (“Farewell Amor”) as mayoral candidate Bella Reál; with Andy Serkis (the “Planet of the Apes” films, “Black Panther”) as Alfred; and Colin Farrell (“Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them,” “Dumbo”) as Oswald Cobblepot.

“The Batman” was written by Matt Reeves & Peter Craig.  Reeves and Dylan Clark (the “Planet of the Apes” films) are producing the film, with Simon Emanuel, Michael E. Uslan, Walter Hamada and Chantal Nong Vo serving as executive producers.  Reeves’ behind-the-scenes creative team includes Oscar-nominated director of photography Greig Fraser (“Lion,” upcoming “Dune”); his “Planet of the Apes” production designer, James Chinlund; editors William Hoy (the “Planet of the Apes” films) and Tyler Nelson (“Rememory”); Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (“The Jungle Book”); Oscar-nominated SFX supervisor Dominic Tuohy (“1917,” “Star Wars: Episode IX – The Rise of Skywalker”); Oscar-nominated sound mixer Stuart Wilson (“1917,” the “Star Wars” franchise); Oscar-winning costume designer Jacqueline Durran (“1917,” “Little Women,” “Anna Karenina”) and costume designers Glyn Dillon (the “Star Wars” franchise) and David Crossman (“1917,” the “Star Wars” franchise); hair designer Zoe Tahir (upcoming “No Time to Die,” “Spectre”); and Oscar-nominated makeup designer Naomi Donne (“1917”).

Based on characters from DC.  Batman was created by Bob Kane with Bill Finger.  “The Batman” is set to open in theaters October 1, 2021 in select 3D and 2D and IMAX theaters and will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Wonder Woman 1984 - Official Main Trailer
snippet.description:
The new era of Wonder Woman begins here. #WW84 only in theaters.
 
http://www.facebook.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://twitter.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://www.instagram.com/wonderwomanfilm
http://wonderwoman1984.com
 
Fast forward to the 1980s as Wonder Woman’s next big screen adventure finds her facing two all-new foes: Max Lord and The Cheetah.  
 
With director Patty Jenkins back at the helm and Gal Gadot returning in the title role, “Wonder Woman 1984” is Warner Bros. Pictures’ follow up to the DC Super Hero’s first outing, 2017’s record-breaking “Wonder Woman,” which took in $822 million at the worldwide box office.  The film also stars Chris Pine as Steve Trevor, Kristen Wiig as The Cheetah, Pedro Pascal as Max Lord, Robin Wright as Antiope, and Connie Nielsen as Hippolyta.
 
Charles Roven, Deborah Snyder, Zack Snyder, Patty Jenkins, Gal Gadot and Stephen Jones are producing the film.  Rebecca Steel Roven Oakley, Richard Suckle, Marianne Jenkins, Geoff Johns, Walter Hamada, Chantal Nong Vo and Wesley Coller are the executive producers.
 
Patty Jenkins directed from a screenplay she wrote with Geoff Johns & David Callaham, story by Jenkins & Johns, based on characters from DC.  Joining the director behind the scenes are several members of her “Wonder Woman” team, including director of photography Matthew Jensen, Oscar-nominated production designer Aline Bonetto (“Amélie”), and Oscar-winning costume designer Lindy Hemming (“Topsy-Turvy”).  Oscar-nominated editor Richard Pearson (“United 93”) is cutting the film.  The music is by Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer (“Dunkirk,” “The Lion King”).
 
Warner Bros. Pictures Presents an Atlas Entertainment/Stone Quarry Production, a Patty Jenkins Film, “Wonder Woman 1984.”  Set to open in theaters in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX, it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.
 
This film is rated PG-13 for sequences of action and violence.

snippet.title: BEST FRIEND KO NOON, STEPMOM KO NGAYON!
snippet.description:
MAHALAGANG PAALALA:


Muli po naming pinapaalala na hanggang ngayon ay SARADO PA RIN PO ANG AMING ACTION CENTER sa TV5 Media Center, Reliance Street, Mandaluyong City.


Hindi pa rin po maaaring pumunta nang personal ang mga complainant para magreklamo kay Idol Raffy dahil sa ating kinahaharap na pandemya at mahigpit pa ring ipinapatupad ang mga safety measures upang maging ligtas ang lahat.


Gayunpaman, puwede ninyong i-PM ang inyong mga sumbong sa OFFICIAL Facebook page ni Idol na RAFFY TULFO IN ACTION na may mahigit 10M followers. Nakahanda pong tumugon sa inyo ang RTIA researchers.


Maraming salamat sa inyong pag-unawa at mag-ingat po tayong lahat!

snippet.title: Wonder Woman 1984 - Official Main Trailer
snippet.description:
The new era of Wonder Woman begins here. #WW84 only in theaters.
 
http://www.facebook.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://twitter.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://www.instagram.com/wonderwomanfilm
http://wonderwoman1984.com
 
Fast forward to the 1980s as Wonder Woman’s next big screen adventure finds her facing two all-new foes: Max Lord and The Cheetah.  
 
With director Patty Jenkins back at the helm and Gal Gadot returning in the title role, “Wonder Woman 1984” is Warner Bros. Pictures’ follow up to the DC Super Hero’s first outing, 2017’s record-breaking “Wonder Woman,” which took in $822 million at the worldwide box office.  The film also stars Chris Pine as Steve Trevor, Kristen Wiig as The Cheetah, Pedro Pascal as Max Lord, Robin Wright as Antiope, and Connie Nielsen as Hippolyta.
 
Charles Roven, Deborah Snyder, Zack Snyder, Patty Jenkins, Gal Gadot and Stephen Jones are producing the film.  Rebecca Steel Roven Oakley, Richard Suckle, Marianne Jenkins, Geoff Johns, Walter Hamada, Chantal Nong Vo and Wesley Coller are the executive producers.
 
Patty Jenkins directed from a screenplay she wrote with Geoff Johns & David Callaham, story by Jenkins & Johns, based on characters from DC.  Joining the director behind the scenes are several members of her “Wonder Woman” team, including director of photography Matthew Jensen, Oscar-nominated production designer Aline Bonetto (“Amélie”), and Oscar-winning costume designer Lindy Hemming (“Topsy-Turvy”).  Oscar-nominated editor Richard Pearson (“United 93”) is cutting the film.  The music is by Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer (“Dunkirk,” “The Lion King”).
 
Warner Bros. Pictures Presents an Atlas Entertainment/Stone Quarry Production, a Patty Jenkins Film, “Wonder Woman 1984.”  Set to open in theaters in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX, it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.
 
This film is rated PG-13 for sequences of action and violence.

snippet.title: Trump angers New Zealand with Covid-19 'big surge' comments as Ardern hits back
snippet.description:
Donald Trump has called out New Zealand for its recent Covid-19 outbreak, saying places once hailed as a success story in the pandemic are now facing a 'big surge' in cases. However, New Zealand's prime minister, Jacinda Ardern, said there was 'no comparison' between the situation there and that in in the US

localizations.fr.title: Les Royaumes Guerriers de la Fourmi Tisserande
localizations.fr.description:
Obtenez Curiosity stream pour seulement $14.99 (12,59€) pour L’ANNÉE entière ou seulement $2.99 (2,51€) par mois: https://curiositystream.com/kurzgesagt

Sources et lecture approfondie:
https://sites.google.com/view/sourcesweaverants

Profondément dans les jungles tropicales reposent des royaumes flottants dirigés par des maîtres magnifiques et mortels: Ce sont en quelque sorte les hauts elfes des royaumes fourmis: Des architectes talentueux qui créent des châteaux et des cités états. Mais ce sont aussi de violents guerriers expansionnistes et leurs royaumes sont piégés dans une guerre sans fin pour la survie.  Les Oecophylla smaragdina.

snippet.title: Oklahoma City Thunder vs Houston Rockets | August 31, 2020
snippet.description: Led by Chris Paul’s 28 points (15 in the 4th quarter), 7 rebounds and 3 assists, the Thunder defeated the Rockets, 104-100, in Game 6. Additionally for the Thunder, Danilo Gallinari added 25 points and 5 rebounds in the victory, while James Harden tallied 32 points, 8 rebounds and 7 assists for the Rockets in the losing effort. This best-of-seven series is now tied, 3-3. Game 7 will take place on Wednesday, September 2 at 9:00 p.m. ET

snippet.title: Israel Adesanya, Paulo Costa get HEATED in interview before UFC 253 fight | SportsCenter
snippet.description:
UFC middleweight champion Israel Adesanya and Paulo Costa chat with Michael Eaves on SportsCenter weeks before their scheduled fight at UFC 253. Both fighters discuss their preparations in the time of COVID-19, how it has affected their families and if their schedules are getting changed at all. They then get heated, calling each other "weak," "dumb" and much more.

snippet.title: Entrevista completa com Flordelis | Conexão Repórter (31/08/20)
snippet.description:
Flordelis dos Santos de Souza quebra o silêncio e fala com exclusividade ao Conexão Repórter. Roberto Cabrini fica frente a frente com a peça central do crime que revela uma complexa trama de traições, sexo, magia negra, dinheiro e poder. Essa é a primeira entrevista da pastora e deputada federal após ser denunciada como mandante do assassinato do marido.

O jornalístico apresenta as declarações de Flordelis, realizadas em dois dias, e em diferentes cenários, em mais de quatro horas de gravações. O programa retrata a trajetória de ascensão e o início da queda da mulher de 59 anos, que tem 55 filhos entre biológicos e adotados, e um império de igrejas construído ao lado do pastor Anderson do Carmo.

A parlamentar aceita acompanhar Cabrini ao local do crime e mostra com exclusividade a casa de 30 quartos e 3 anexos, além de reconstituir, lado a lado com o repórter, os detalhes daquela noite. O telespectador vai ver o que ela tem a dizer sobre a série de mensagens enviadas de seu telefone para seus filhos, onde fala do marido sempre em tons pejorativos, em trama tão complexa que resultou no indiciamento de 11 pessoas, das quais apenas a pastora está em liberdade.

O São Paulo jogou na manhã deste domingo (30) no Morumbi contra o Corinthians, por partida válida pelo Campeonato Brasileiro 2020 e venceu por 2 a 1, com gols de Hernanes, de falta, e de Brenner, nos acréscimos do segundo tempo.

-

INSCREVA-SE no canal oficial São Paulo FC: http://goo.gl/mXCkhI

youtube.com/spfctv - Desde 2008 levando os bastidores do Tricolor aos torcedores!

snippet.title: Clash Royale: ⚔️ COMEÇA A GUERRA DE CLÃS 2! ⚔️ (Trailer Oficial de Lançamento)
snippet.description:
NOVA ATUALIZAÇÃO GUERRA DE CLÃS 2!
- Navegue com seu barco do clã em busca de recompensas e glória
- Junte-se à Corrida de Barcos e enfrente outros clãs para obter grandes recompensas
- Configure suas defesas de barco e ataque outros do clã em batalhas navais
- Construa 4 decks de guerra e enfrente outros jogadores em duelos épicos

Prepare-se para Guerra de Clãs 2!

Inscreva-se para mais! ►► https://supr.cl/SubRoyaleBR

Entre na Arena! Dos criadores do Clash of Clans, o Clash Royale é um jogo multijogador em tempo real que traz os Royales, seus personagens preferidos do Clash e muito mais!

Colecione e melhore dezenas de cartas com as tropas, feitiços e defesas do Clash of Clans que você já conhece e adora, além dos Royales: Príncipe, Cavaleiro, Bebê Dragão e muito mais. Destrua as torres do rei e das princesas rivais para derrotar seu oponente e ganhar troféus, coroas e muita glória na arena. Forme um clã para doar e receber cartas, além de construir sua própria comunidade de batalha.

Leve a Família Clash Royale à vitória!

RECURSOS
● Batalhe com jogadores do mundo inteiro em tempo real e ganhe troféus.
● Ganhe baús e use-os para desbloquear recompensas, colecionar novas cartas poderosas e melhorar as cartas que já possui.
● Destrua as torres do seu oponente e ganhe coroas para abrir baús da coroa épicos.
● Construa e melhore sua coleção de cartas com a Família Clash Royale e dezenas das suas tropas, feitiços e defesas favoritos do Clash.
● Construa um forte deck de batalha para derrotar seus oponentes.
● Avance no jogo e desbloqueie várias arenas até chegar ao topo.
● Forme um clã para doar e receber cartas, além de construir sua própria comunidade de batalha.
● Desafie seus colegas de clã e amigos em um duelo privado.
● Assista aos melhores duelos na TV Royale e aprenda diferentes estratégias de batalha.

ATENÇÃO! O Clash Royale é grátis para baixar e jogar, porém alguns itens do jogo também podem ser adquiridos por meio de compras com dinheiro real. Caso não queira utilizar esse recurso, você pode desabilitar as compras do aplicativo nas configurações do seu dispositivo. Além disso, de acordo com os nossos Termos de Uso e Política de Privacidade, você deve ter no mínimo 13 anos de idade para poder jogar e baixar o Clash Royale. Uma conexão de rede também é necessária para jogar.

Suporte:
Está com problemas? Visite https://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clash-royale/?p=web&l=pt ou entre em contato conosco por meio do jogo. Para isso, acesse Configurações e toque em Ajuda e suporte.

Política de Privacidade
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/pt/

Termos de Uso:
http://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/pt/

Guia para os Pais
http://supercell.com/en/parents/ (em inglês).

snippet.title: Se Liga Na Educação - Linguagens - 31/08/20
snippet.description:
Após as aulas, os vídeos estarão disponíveis no canal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTAE3t96gJbgn1K-0yaPV2Q 

O Programa Se Liga na Educação é uma iniciativa da Secretaria de Estado de Educação, apoiada pela Rede Minas e é parte do Regime de Estudo Não Presencial. 

Vai exibir aulas com conteúdos dos diferentes componentes curriculares, divididos por grupos de disciplinas e voltadas para cada ano de escolaridade. O objetivo é levar conteúdos escolares aos alunos da rede pública, neste momento em que as atividades presenciais estão suspensas e as escolas fechadas por causa da pandemia do coronavírus.  

https://estudeemcasa.educacao.mg.gov.br/se-liga-na-educacao

Horário
Vai ao ar de 7h30 a 12h30, de segunda a sexta-feira.

As aulas são posteriormente disponibilizadas separadamente no aplicativo "Conexão Escola" e no canal do YouTube da Secretaria de Estado de Educação (http://youtube.com/estudioeducacaomg).

snippet.title: Die Abschleppbrüder vom Autobahnkreuz | die nordreportage | NDR Doku
snippet.description:
Die Brüder Oliver und Rouven Flörke sind Abschleppunternehmer, 24 Stunden erreichbar und am Lehrter Kreuz zwischen der A2 und A7 unterwegs, zwei der meistbefahrenen Autobahnen in Deutschland. Die beiden leiten seit einem Jahr gemeinsam das Familienunternehmen mit 20 Mitarbeitenden. Doch der Seniorchef, ihr Vater, kann sich immer noch nicht so ganz trennen.

Mit Sorge betrachten die Brüder die Entwicklung auf den Autobahnen. Ihr Eindruck: Trotz aller Prävention und vermehrter Kontrollen, gibt es immer mehr Autobahnunfälle mit schweren Personenschäden. Autobahneinsätze sind auch für die Abschlepper gefährlich, denn sie arbeiten dann oft im fließenden Verkehr.

"Die Nordreportage" begleitet das Brüderpaar während des Ferienverkehrs in ihrem ersten gemeinsamen Jahr als Leiter des Unternehmens.

Mehr dazu: 
https://www.ndr.de/fernsehen/sendungen/die_nordreportage/Die-Abschleppbrueder-vom-Autobahnkreuz,sendung1066880.html

#ndr #doku #autobahn

____________________________________________________
Ich bin Ana Johnson, 27 Jahre alt, social-media Künstlerin und lebe in Köln.
Seit ca. drei Jahren mache ich verschiedenste Social-Media-Plattformen unsicher. Ich bin ein kleiner Perfektionist und liebe Details! Daher gibt es besonders bei meinen Instagramfotos viel zu entdecken. Manchmal reichen Fotos oder kurze Instagramstorys nicht aus. Dafür liebe ich YouTube! Hier zeige ich euch Updates zum Hausbau, Einrichtungstipps, Inspirationen für eure nächste Reise, Tipps für eure Haare oder Haut, Make-up und natürlich Unterhaltung, in meinem Podcast zu hören und auf meinem Blog zu lesen!!

snippet.title: JP Kraemer rast mit 142 km/h innerorts - Trotzdem straflos? | Rechtsanwalt Christian Solmecke
snippet.description:
Viele von euch werden das YT-Video von JP Kraemer kennen, der innerorts 142 km/h, also 92 km/h über der erlaubten Geschwindigkeit, gefahren ist, und sich dabei gefilmt hat. Im Internet waren sich die meisten von euch einig: So ein Verhalten muss bestraft werden. Tatsächlich hat die zuständige Staatsanwaltschaft die Ermittlungen jedoch eingestellt. Der Grund sind Auslegungsprobleme rund um den so genannten Raserparagraphen § 315d StGB, den es erst seit kurzem gibt. Was es damit auf sich hat und ob JP Kraemer jetzt tatsächlich davon kommt, erfahrt ihr in diesem Video.

Rechtsanwalt Christian Solmecke
Christian Solmecke hat sich als Rechtsanwalt und Partner der Kölner Medienrechtskanzlei WILDE BEUGER SOLMECKE auf die Beratung der Internet-, IT- und Medienbranche spezialisiert. So hat er in den vergangenen Jahren den Bereich Internetrecht/E-Commerce der Kanzlei stetig ausgebaut und betreut zahlreiche Medienschaffende, Web 2.0 Plattformen und App-Entwickler.
Neben seiner Kanzleitätigkeit ist Solmecke Geschäftsführer des Deutschen Instituts für Kommunikation und Recht im Internet an der Cologne Business School (http://www.dikri.de). Dort beschäftigt er sich insbesondere mit den Rechtsfragen in Sozialen Netzen. Vor seiner Tätigkeit als Anwalt arbeitete er über 10 Jahre als freier Journalist und Radiomoderator (u.a. für den Westdeutschen Rundfunk).

Im Mittelpunkt werden Instagram-Stories mit all den inzwischen vorhandenen Funktionen wie z.B. Quizelementen stehen. Dazu begleitend: Instagram-Posts und IGTV-Langvideos. Aha-Momente sind vorprogrammiert! Folge uns auf Recht2Go und du kannst vor deinen Freunden mit neuem Wissen glänzen. Hier der Link:

snippet.title: Weiß Connor über Kim & Mike Bescheid?!😱😰 | Berlin - Tag & Nacht #2268
snippet.description:
Toni möchte wissen, in welchem Verhältnis Kim nun mit Mike steht. Als sie heimlich darüber reden, platzt plötzlich Connor ins Zimmer. Kim hat Angst, dass er womöglich etwas mitbekommen hat. Denn Connor darf niemals erfahren, dass sie etwas mit seinem Vater hatte!

Die gescriptete Reality-Soap „Berlin - Tag & Nacht“ zeigt die coolste WG Berlins, mit Themen wie  Freundschaft, Liebe,  Eifersucht, Affären, Glück, Freude und Leiden. Wie im echten Leben eben!
Alte wie neue WG-Bewohner, u. a. Ole, Joe, Peggy, Krätze, Schmidti, Eule, Basti Paula, Piet, Milla, Leon und viele weitere, zeigen dir ihr Leben in Berlin, der bunten Metropole Deutschlands. Sie nehmen dich mit in ihre Wohngemeinschaften, auf ihre Arbeitsplätze, in den Club Matrix, den Friseursalon „Schnitte“ sowie die Bar LA 14. Auch ein Tattoostudio und das Fitnessstudio Body Burn gehören zu den unterschiedlichen und wechselnden Handlungsorten der Serie. Die Großstadt-Soap „Berlin – Tag & Nacht“ ist nicht zuletzt deshalb so beliebt, weil sie die Bewohner der WGs im Ringen mit alltäglichen Problemen zeigt: Affäre und Eifersucht, Erfolgsdruck im Beruf sowie viele zwischenmenschliche Konflikte. 

"Berlin - Tag & Nacht" läuft Montag bis Freitag um 19:05 Uhr bei RTLZWEI.

snippet.title: DAS ist das gefährlichste Tier Deutschlands! | Bundeswehr
snippet.description:
Sie sind blutrünstig und können den Tod bringen. Sie sind kaum sichtbar und lauern im Verborgenen. Sie sind zu Recht unbeliebt und extrem gefährlich – #ZECKEN! Als #Parasiten brauchen sie andere Lebewesen, von deren Blut sie sich ernähren – ähnlich wie Stechmücken. Doch im Vergleich zu Stechmücken brauchen Zecken viel mehr Blut. Im Extremfall hängen sie bis zu zwei Wochen an ihrem Wirt (Tiere und Menschen) und trinken dessen Blut. Ist eine Zecke mit Krankheitserregern infiziert, kann auch ein an und für sich harmloser Zeckenstich für Menschen gefährlich werden. Gemeinsam mit Oberfeldarzt Professor Dr. Gerhard Dobler gehen wir den Parasiten auf den Grund. Der Zecken-Experte erklärt unter anderem, wie wir uns schützen können, wie Zecken richtig entfernt werden und welche nicht zu unterschätzende Gefahr für Soldaten besteht. 

Willst du mehr über Tiere wissen? Hier findest du weitere Videos:

Umgang mit gefährlichen Tieren bei der Bundeswehr
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PdzrWgaYibk

Wölfe – bedroht oder bedrohlich? 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ra6GkrZGWzo

#FSME

snippet.title: Gefangen im Feuer!🔥😲 #1939 | Köln 50667
snippet.description:
Meike hat Oskars Drogen gefunden und Ben sofort informiert. Doch der kann es nicht fassen, dass Oskar wirklich so tief gesunken ist. Oskar kann sich durch einen Nebenjob im Kuen etwas Ablenkung verschaffen und auch Meike hofft, dass er dadurch wieder zur Vernunft kommt. Doch als Lea während seiner Arbeit aufkreuzt und mit ihm reden will, taucht Oskars aggressives Verhalten wieder auf. Eigentlich hatte Meike gehofft, dass Oskar sich durch den Nebenjob im Kuen seiner Verantwortung stellen kann, doch als er eine wichtige Lieferung vermasselt, schmeißt Meike Oskar und Samantha raus. Nachdem Oskar auch seinen Nebenjob im Kuen verloren und von Meike zur Sau gemacht wurde, betrinkt er sich mit Samantha in einem leerstehenden Gebäude seinen Frust von der Seele. Doch dabei merken die beiden nicht, dass sie in Lebensgefahr schweben...

snippet.title: Corona-Demo in Berlin: Diese klaren Worte findet Schauspieler Jan Josef Liefers zur Corona-Krise
snippet.description:
Tauche mit unserer Doku tief in die Welt der Verschwörungstheoretiker und ihrer gestörten Fantasien ein: https://bit.ly/2YJNDxl

Der Schauspieler, der 1989 gegen die DDR-Diktatur und für Demokratie und Freiheit auf die Straße ging, fühlte sich am Wochenende an das Wendejahr erinnert. Der große Unterschied: Damals habe man ein großes gemeinsames Ziel gehabt, am Wochenende habe es so viele Meinungen gegeben, dass „keine richtige Wirkung und Richtung“ entfaltet wurde.

Aber: Zwischen Verschwörungstheoretikern und Rechtsradikalen habe es auch Menschen gegeben, die schlicht und ergreifend große Angst um ihre Existenz haben!

Das Problem, so Liefers: Jeder, der seine Zweifel an den staatlichen Corona-Maßnahmen äußert, „wird sofort in Ecken geschubst.“

#corona #demo #berlin #covid-19

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔴  Abonniert jetzt unseren Kanal und aktiviert die Glocke!

🎥  V-Mann „Miami Gianni“ packt aus: Undercover zwischen Zuhältern, Rockern und Clans – die BILDplus-Doku: https://on.bild.de/3dZGq0K
🎥  „Blinder Hass – Wie wird ein normaler Junge zum Killer-Neonazi?“ – die BILDplus-Doku über den Halle-Attentäter Stephan Balliet: https://on.bild.de/39fSLgK
🎥  Die besten Dokus mit BILDplus gibt's hier: https://on.bild.de/BILDvideothek

📲  Folgt unseren Moderatoren:
Nele Würzbach https://www.instagram.com/nele.wuerzbach
Moritz Wedel https://www.instagram.com/moritzwedel
Sina Stinshoff https://www.instagram.com/sina_stinshoff

👁‍🗨  Impressum: https://on.bild.de/impressum

#BILD #Nachrichten #News

snippet.title: Fard über 15 Jahre im Deutschrap, Beef mit Sido, Battle Rap, Life is Pain & Features mit US-Rappern
snippet.description:
Gerade erst am 28. August hat Fard sein neues Album “Nazizi” veröffentlicht, nun beehrt er uns bei Baked. Er spricht mit Marvin Game über seinen brandaktuellen Release und blickt zurück auf verschiedene Aspekte aus 15 Jahren Rapkarriere im Deutschrap. Fard spricht über die Anfänge seiner legendären Karriere im Battle Rap und Freestyle, über “Blut, Schweiß, Tränen & Triumphe”, vergebene Beefs mit Sido, Karriereentscheidungen und die Arbeit mit dem Label “Life is Pain”, für das er als Labelmanager tätig ist.

Kanal abonnieren: http://bit.ly/2VNIpjH

Geçici bu öfke, bu hırs, bu intikam
